Title: Locally Resolvable  
Author: Carlos Gonzalez-Ochoa George Vanecek Jr. 
Keyword: Collision detection, multiple levels-of-detail, data structures, boundary repre sentations.  
Web: 60NANB4D1645. http://www.cs.purdue.edu/people/gonzalez http://www.cs.purdue.edu/people/vanecek  
